column5: Packed and leaving early tomorrow morning for Brace Lake!6 am flight in on Sunday morning and one week of pure heaven! The weather report is positive with temps in the 70s. There will be no sleeping tonight.

I have to wait 4 more weeks! I was in communication with them last year inquiring. I cannot remember the girls name right now (Terri maybe), but she was super to deal with. Anyway they seem very into their job, so I would expect super service. Look forward to report on your return.
